N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 603.10 - Decision of the commission

State Regulations

The decision of the commission shall be in writing, signed
by the commissioners and sealed. It shall be filed in the office of the
commission. Certified copies of the decision shall be sent by the commission to
the parties in the case. Notes
